org.eclipse.eef

Interface EEFWidgetDescription

  • All Superinterfaces:
    EEFControlDescription, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    EEFButtonDescription, EEFCheckboxDescription, EEFCustomWidgetDescription, EEFHyperlinkDescription, EEFLabelDescription, EEFListDescription, EEFRadioDescription, EEFSelectDescription, EEFTextDescription
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EEFButtonDescriptionImpl, EEFCheckboxDescriptionImpl, EEFCustomWidgetDescriptionImpl, EEFHyperlinkDescriptionImpl, EEFLabelDescriptionImpl, EEFListDescriptionImpl, EEFRadioDescriptionImpl, EEFSelectDescriptionImpl, EEFTextDescriptionImpl, EEFWidgetDescriptionImpl

    public interface EEFWidgetDescription
extends EEFControlDescription
    A representation of the model object 'EEF Widget Description'. Graphical element.

    The following features are supported:

    • Label Expression
    • Help Expression
    • Is Enabled Expression
    • Property Validation Rules
    See Also:
    EefPackage.getEEFWidgetDescription()
